

jtsocket
=========

JTSocket is part of the Terca Java Libraries.
Terca Java Sockets provide a very basic TCP server and client.
It uses a variety of defaults in order to simplify usage.
It is not designed to be multithreaded as this time.

Dependencies
============

JTSocket uses the Bouncy Castle cryptography library.
This is provided through maven automatically.
